---
import { CldImage } from 'astro-cloudinary';
import LADExperiment from '../features/LADExperiment.astro';
---
      <!-- LAD Experiment Section -->
      <section class='relative py-20 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden' id='lad-section'>
        <!-- Background Glow -->
        <!-- Background Glow (hidden on mobile to prevent hard edges from overflow clipping) -->
        <div
          class='hidden md:block absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] translate-x-1/2 pointer-events-none'
        >
        </div>

        <div class='page-container relative z-10'>
          <!-- 1. The Hook: 30-Second Test -->
          <div class='text-center max-w-192 mx-auto mb-16'>
            <div
              class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm font-medium text-white mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm'
            >
              <span class='animate-pulse text-yellow-400'>â±ï¸</span>
              <span>Tes 30 Detik</span>
            </div>

            <h2
              class='text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight'
            >
              Buktikan Sendiri dalam 30 Detik: Kamu Punya <span
                class='text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400'
                >"Insting Bahasa"</span
              > yang Kuat Banget.
            </h2>
            <p class='text-lg text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed'>
              Jangan cuma percaya omongan kami. Yuk, kita buktiin bareng-bareng
              sekarang jugaâ€”cuma butuh 30 detik doang. Kami yakin kamu bakal
              langsung ngerasain "wah, bener juga" sendiri.
              <br /><br />
              Baca dua kalimat Bahasa Indonesia ini pelan-pelan:
            </p>
          </div>

          <LADExperiment />

          <!-- 3. Immediate Reaction Text -->
          <div
            class='w-full mx-auto text-center mb-24 hidden lad-reaction opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-700'
            style='max-width: 48rem;'
          >
            <p
              class='text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white font-medium leading-relaxed'
            >
              <span class='text-emerald-400'>"Wah, bener juga."</span><br />
              Tanpa buka buku tata bahasa, tanpa mikir S-P-O-K atau aturan apa pun...
              kamu langsung ngerasa kalimat nomor 2 itu aneh banget, kan?
            </p>
            <div class='w-full mx-auto mt-4' style='max-width: 42rem;'>
              <p class='text-lg text-(--token-text-secondary)'>
                Rasanya "nggak enak" dibaca, kayak ada yang salah, meskipun kamu
                masih bisa nangkep maksudnya secara kasar (lupa dompet pas mau
                beli takoyaki).
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 4. The Deep Dive (Grid) -->
          <div class='grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-20 items-start mb-24'>
            <div
              class='lg:col-span-5 order-2 lg:order-1 sticky top-32 hidden lg:block'
            >
              <div
                class='relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white/10 group'
              >
                <CldImage
                  src='LAD_Generated_Image_16yr3x16yr3x16yr_ygwtpf'
                  alt='Visualisasi Language Acquisition Device (LAD)'
                  width={1000}
                  height={1000}
                  crop='fill'
                  class='w-full h-auto transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-in-out'
                />
                <div
                  class='absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60'
                >
                </div>
                <div class='absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6'>
                  <div
                    class='text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-white/70 uppercase mb-1'
                  >
                    Konsep
                  </div>
                  <div class='text-lg font-bold text-white'>
                    The Language Acquisition Device
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class='lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-8'>
              <div
                class='relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden p-6 md:p-8 border border-white/10 shadow-2xl bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,#0c080c_0%,transparent_100%)]'
              >
                <!-- Purple Ambient Spotlight -->
                <div
                  class='absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,rgba(168,85,247,0.15)_0%,transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none'
                >
                </div>
                <h3 class='text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6'>
                  Kenapa kamu langsung tahu itu salah dan terasa janggal? ğŸ¤”
                </h3>
                <div
                  class='space-y-6 text-lg text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed'
                >
                  <p>
                    Bukan karena kamu hafal rumus grammar Indonesia dari SD.
                    Kamu tahu karena kamu punya <strong class='text-purple-400'
                      >insting bahasa alami</strong
                    > yang disebut <span class='text-white'
                      >Language Acquisition Device (LAD)</span
                    > oleh Prof. Chomskyâ€”semacam "perangkat bawaan" di otak manusia
                    yang aktif sejak lahir untuk menyerap bahasa secara intuitif lewat
                    paparan terus-menerus.
                  </p>

                  <!-- Mobile-only LAD Image -->
                  <div class='lg:hidden my-6'>
                    <div
                      class='relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-white/10'
                    >
                      <CldImage
                        src='LAD_Generated_Image_16yr3x16yr3x16yr_ygwtpf'
                        alt='Visualisasi Language Acquisition Device (LAD)'
                        width={800}
                        height={800}
                        crop='fill'
                        class='w-full h-auto'
                      />
                      <div
                        class='absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/80 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-60'
                      >
                      </div>
                      <div class='absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4'>
                        <div
                          class='text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-white/70 uppercase mb-1'
                        >
                          Konsep
                        </div>
                        <div class='text-base font-bold text-white'>
                          The Language Acquisition Device
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <p>
                    LAD ini yang bikin kamu otomatis "merasa" mana kalimat yang
                    natural dan mana yang pincang, tanpa perlu analisa rumus.
                  </p>
                  <div
                    class='p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 my-6'
                  >
                    <p class='text-base italic text-white/80'>
                      "Kalimat nomor 2 itu sengaja kami bikin mirip kayak
                      terjemahan mentah-mentah dari orang Jepang yang lagi
                      belajar Bahasa Indonesiaâ€”mereka nerjemahin kata per kata
                      sesuai struktur Jepang, jadi urutannya campur aduk,
                      partikelnya ngawur..."
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <p>
                    Kamu masih bisa paham maksudnya (karena konteksnya jelas),
                    tapi rasanya "off" banget, unsettling, kayak denger orang
                    ngomong tapi agak pincang.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 5. The Conclusion / Bridge -->
          <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12'>
            <!-- Success Box -->
            <div
              class='relative p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-br from-purple-900/40 to-indigo-900/40 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden'
            >
              <div
                class='absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] pointer-events-none'
              >
              </div>
              <div
                class='relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-center'
              >
                <div class='shrink-0 p-4 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-4xl'>
                  ğŸŒ±
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class='text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4'>
                    Selamat! Kamu baru saja buktiin sendiri.
                  </h4>
                  <p
                    class='text-lg text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed'
                  >
                    LAD di otakmu masih aktif dan super kuat. Perangkat bawaan
                    itu udah jalan lancar buat Bahasa Indonesia sejak kamu
                    kecil.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- The Problem & Solution -->
            <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-12'>
              <div class='space-y-4'>
                <h4
                  class='text-xl font-bold text-red-400 flex items-center gap-2'
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                    width='20'
                    height='20'
                    viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                    fill='none'
                    stroke='currentColor'
                    stroke-width='2'
                    stroke-linecap='round'
                    stroke-linejoin='round'
                    class='lucide lucide-x-circle'
                    ><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10'></circle><path d='m15 9-6 6'
                    ></path><path d='m9 9 6 6'></path></svg
                  >
                  Masalahnya di bahasa Jepang?
                </h4>
                <p class='text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed'>
                  Metode tradisional (hafal bunpou dulu, terjemahin dulu) justru <strong
                    >mematikan LAD itu</strong
                  > sebelum dia sempat bekerja optimal. Mereka paksa kamu mikir lewat
                  rumus (surface structure), bukan lewat insting alami (deep structure).
                  Akibatnya, intuisi nativemu buat Jepang nggak pernah terbentukâ€”kamu
                  jadi gagap, loading lama, dan bahasa keluarnya kaku.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class='space-y-4'>
                <h4
                  class='text-xl font-bold text-emerald-400 flex items-center gap-2'
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                    width='20'
                    height='20'
                    viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                    fill='none'
                    stroke='currentColor'
                    stroke-width='2'
                    stroke-linecap='round'
                    stroke-linejoin='round'
                    class='lucide lucide-check-circle'
                    ><path d='M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14'
                    ></path><polyline points='22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01'
                    ></polyline></svg
                  >
                  Metode Solusi & Komunitas Immersion
                </h4>
                <p class='text-(--token-text-secondary) leading-relaxed'>
                  Kami cuma mengaktifkan kembali LAD yang samaâ€”yang udah
                  terbukti works di Bahasa Indonesia kamuâ€”buat bahasa Jepang.
                  Caranya? Dengan kasih <strong>comprehensible input</strong> yang
                  pas, sampai LAD-mu bangun intuisi nativenya sendiri secara alami.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>